My Game:

Take care of chickens for the day. 
  at 4:00am let them out of the coop in the morning, 
  at 8:00am feed the chickens,
  at 12:00pm, check the coop for eggs,
  at 1:00pm, clean the coop, 
  at 6:00pm, put them back in the coop at night. 
Avoid letting the chickens out, or letting predators in. Dont let the rooster be
bossy.

